    "slot_size": 238,
    "data_size": 234,
    "nom_orig": "Tamaki",
    "texte_orig": "Also,[SP]you[SP]can[SP]only[SP]send[SP]in[SP]99[SP]magazines[SP]per\nentry.[SP]The[SP]more[SP]you[SP]send,[SP]the[SP]better[SP]your\nchances[SP]of[SP]winning.",
