    "data_size": 264,
    "nom_orig": "Tamaki",
    "texte_orig": "Finally,[SP]it[SP]takes[SP]time[SP]for[SP]the[SP]results[SP]to\ncome[SP]in.[SP]You[SP]can't[SP]just[SP]sit[SP]around[SP]and[SP]wait.\nYou[SP]have[SP]to[SP]walk[SP]around[SP]dungeons.",
