    "texte_orig": "Hehehe,[SP]whaddaya[SP]think[SP]of[SP]my[SP]poster?[SP]It's[SP]Muses!\nA[SP]genuine[SP]Muses[SP]poster![SP]You[SP]know[SP]about[SP]Muses,\nright?",
