    "texte_orig": "Right?\n[U+1208][0002]Yes\nNo\n[U+1109][E2][E3][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Tadashi\nHehehe...[SP]What[SP]can[SP]I[SP]say?[SP]I'm[SP]a[SP]red-blooded\nmale[SP]and[SP]a[SP]sucker[SP]for[SP]cute[SP]girls.[SP]I[SP]hope[SP]they\nreveal[SP]the[SP]third[SP]girl[SP]soon...",
