    "data_size": 280,
    "nom_orig": "Tadashi",
    "texte_orig": "You[SP]just[SP]can't[SP]buy[SP]a[SP]poster[SP]like[SP]this.[SP]It's\na[SP]valuable[SP]memento[SP]I[SP]only[SP]got[SP]through[SP]my\ndetective[SP]skills.[SP]You[SP]better[SP]not[SP]touch[SP]it.",
