    "texte_orig": "Hmm,[SP]I'm[SP]curious[SP]about[SP]Muses,[SP]but[SP]also[SP]about\nthe[SP]Masked[SP]Circle...[1205][U+000F][SP]I[SP]get[SP]the[SP]feeling[SP]they're\na[SP]dangerous[SP]bunch.",
